dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Peter Hill. May I have your name, please?
Hi Peter, my name is Kelly Rogers.
Thank you, Kelly. Could you please provide me with the license plate number of the vehicle involved in the incident?
Sure, the license plate number is Bravo Tango Foxtrot 4 5 8.
Great, thank you. Can you also confirm the date of the accident in day month year format?
The accident occurred on the second of May, twenty two.
Thank you for the information, Kelly. We will process your claim and provide you with updates as soon as possible. Is there anything else you would like to add?
No, that's all for now. Thank you.
You're welcome, Kelly. Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
Thank you for your time. Goodbye.
